import React from 'react';
import Link from 'next/link'

import {
  ProgramName,
  FieldHeader,
  FieldValue,
  Container,
  CollegeName,
  Logo,
} from './ProgramRow.styles';



const ProgramRow = (program) => {
  console.log(program)

  return(
    <Link href={`/ProgramDetail?id=${program.id}`}>
      <>
      <Logo/>
      <ProgramName>Information Technology</ProgramName>
      <CollegeName>Santa Rosa Junior College</CollegeName>
      <FieldHeader start={4} end={5}>
        Degree Type
      </FieldHeader>
      <FieldValue start={4} end={5}>
        Associate's
      </FieldValue>
      <FieldHeader start={5} end={6}>
        Delivery
      </FieldHeader>
      <FieldValue start={5} end={6}>
        {program.deliveryType}
      </FieldValue>
      <FieldHeader start={6} end={7}>
        Annual Tuition
      </FieldHeader>
      <FieldValue start={6} end={7}>
        $1,375
      </FieldValue>
      </>
    </Link>
  )


};

export default ProgramRow;
